<doc id="300677" wikidata="Q224365" url="?curid=300677" title="Cromwell (disambiguation)">
<text>[[Oliver Cromwell]] (1599–1658) was an English military and political leader and later Lord Protector of the Commonwealth of England, Scotland and Ireland.

Cromwell may also refer to:

==People==
*Cromwell (name)

==Places==
* Cromwell, New South Wales, Australia
* Cromwell, Nottinghamshire, England
* Cromwell, New Zealand

